			<div class="about-hero about-hero_careers">
				<div class="about-hero__title">Become a part of the PixBrowse community. Regardless of your location.</div>
				<div class="about-hero__text">The inception of PixBrowse stemmed from our difficulties in sourcing excellent, utilitarian images, and it became evident that we were not alone in this quest.<br>Today, artists from various corners of the world have already tapped into thousands of PixBrowse images to enhance mockups, presentations, artwork, and a wide range of projects.</div>

			</div>
		</div>
