				<div class="title title_mb">How to Get Started</div>
				<div class="about-us__text">Applying is straightforward—just send us a message if you're interested in working with us. There's no need for a traditional resume. Instead, please introduce yourself and share some of your exciting, pertinent achievements.</div>
				<div class="about-us__text">With substantial plans on the horizon, we're excited to hear from you if you're interested in being a part of our journey.</div>
				<div class="about-us__text">We're eager to connect with individuals who share our vision and are committed to contributing to our mission over the long haul.</div>
